@microsoft is launching a brand new @bing Chat. As your AI-powered copilot for the web, it delivers a world of exploration beyond anything you've experienced before. Bing is as easy as speaking to a friend. You don't need any special training or skills, and you can easily tap into new territory without being an expert. Ask Bing anything and get the real-life answers you need.

This film takes you on a journey of the features and possibilities of the Bing Chat in the familiar Windows 11 experience, available at your fingertips.

Big team effort >>@rhoadsclarke @kiwiperson @mariathemuppet @m.mrvic @shinybinary @microsoft.design 
Sound by @zeligsound

Microsoft Defender is a new premium, consumer “all–in–one” security experience from Microsoft. I was asked to explore a creative direction from splash screen, backgrounds to in-product icons focusing on an emotional resonance that makes
Defender an elegant, easy, and accessible means to secure your digital information.

Defender is weaving the threads of technology, information, and access seamlessly across our devices, protecting our everyday lives through many layers of digital security / capabilities. Because technology has become a part of our DNA, security has shifted from a transactional connection to an emotional one.

Visualizing AI is an initiative by @googledeepmind & @google that aims to open up conversations around AI. Commissioning a diverse range of artists to create open source imagery, the project seeks to make AI more accessible to the general public. Visualizing AI explores the roles and responsibilities of the technology. It weighs up concerns and the societal benefits in a highly original collection of works by world-class creators. From the abstract to the literal, each image is an authentic representation of the artist’s take on AI. Available as part of an open-source library, the collection aims to shift dated perceptions of AI in order for everyone and anyone to have a say on the future of the technology.
Sound & Music Design by @_noi_berlin

The pressure-sensitive stylus pen allows for more precise control over applications, making it much easier to create sophisticated design.
